snippet.title: Rob Deniel - Ikaw Sana (Performance Video)
snippet.description:
#robdeniel #ikawsana #vicormusic
Rob Deniel breathes fresh life into Ogie Alcasid’s timeless hit “Ikaw Sana” with his signature blend of powerful vocals and retro-pop sensibilities. While the original is a heartfelt ballad of longing and unspoken love, Rob’s version wraps it in a youthful glow layered with mellow instrumentation. With this track, Rob Deniel proves that great love songs never age – they simply find fresh voices to tell their story. 

Rob Deniel revitalizes an enduring Ogie Alcasid classic. See his passionate performance of "Ikaw Sana" unvarnished, sentimental, and breathtaking.

Composed by Ogie Alcasid
Published by Viva Music Publishing, Inc.
Produced by Jean-Paul Verona
Arranged by Jhay Alicayos
Recorded by Jean-Paul Verona, Rene Serna, Lia Reoma
Electric Guitars by Jonathan Garcia
Acoustic Guitars by Ken Tiongson
Keyboards by Jhay Alicayos
Bass by Jed Barrinuevo
Drums by Danne Malnegro
Mixed by Jean-Paul Verona
Mastered by Jean-Paul Verona
A&R Manager: Jean-Paul Verona
Artist’s A&R: John Bautista

Executive Producers: Vic del Rosario, Verb del Rosario, Antonio Ocampo
Executive Producer: Vic del Rosario, Verb del Rosario
AVP for Artist Management and Label Relations: 
Sammy Samaniego
Artist Manager and Talent Development Manager: 
Senior Road Manager: Jhoanna Cara
Label Manager: Emerson Abaraccoso 
Assistant Marketing Manager: Ken Opina 
Assistant Manager for Creatives and Production: Kelvin Guzman
YouTube Specialist: Paolo Bautista

Glam Team:
HMUA: Posh Torres
STYLIST: Rodel Brinas and Kimmy Guevarra

Video by: 
Myles Capareda
Kobi Gonzales

LYRICS :
Sa buhay natin
Mayro'ng isang mamahalin, sasambahin
Sa buhay natin
Mayro'ng isang bukod tangi sa lahat at iibigin nang tapat

Ngunit sa 'di inaasahang pagkakataon
Na para bang ika'y nilalaro ng panahon
May ibang makikilala at sa unang pagkikita
May tunay na pag-ibig na madarama

Bakit ba hindi ka nakilala nang ako'y malaya pa
At hindi ngayon ang puso ko may kapiling na
Bakit ba hindi ka nakilala nang ako'y nag-iisa
Sino ang iibigin
Ikaw sana

'Di mo napapansin
Sa bawat oras na kasama mo siya, kapiling ka niya
Bawat sandali
Punung-puno ng ligaya't saya, damdamin ay iba

At sa 'di inaasahang pagkakataon
Na para bang ika'y nilalaro ng panahon
Bigla kayong nagyakap, mga labi nyo'y naglapat
Ang inyong mga mata'y nagtatanong at nangangarap

Bakit ba hindi ka nakilala nang ako'y malaya pa
At hindi ngayon ang puso ko may kapiling na
Bakit ba hindi ka nakilala nang ako'y nag-iisa
Sino ang iibigin
Ikaw sana

Ohh, woah
Bakit ba hindi ka nakilala nang ako'y malaya pa
At hindi ngayon ang puso ko may kapiling na
Bakit ‘di ka nakilala nang ako'y nag-iisa
Sino ang iibigin
Ohh, woah…
Ohh hoh…

Sino ang iibigin
Sino ang iibigin
Ohh, woah

snippet.title: DRX vs. NRG — VALORANT Champions Paris — Group Stage
snippet.description:
Welcome to the climax of the 2025 VALORANT Champions Tour! The biggest stage in VALORANT is ready, the lights of Paris are shining, and the countdown has begun. Following a season of historic rivalries, epic comebacks, and unforgettable moments, the world’s top teams now gather at Champions Paris.

From September 12 to October 5, the journey continues through Group Stage and Playoffs before the epic conclusion at the Grand Final with the crowning of the next World Champion. The Group Stage will feature 16 teams spread across four groups, with each group hosting one team from VALORANT's four International Leagues. In this stage, teams will battle through a double elimination format, advancing two teams out of each group. The 8 teams who make it out will be randomly seeded into a double elimination bracket, with teams from the same group placed on opposite sides of the bracket. Teams will compete through Best-of-3 matches until the final 2 matches which will be a Best-of-5. The last team standing will claim the title of VALORANT World Champion!

We’re proud to work with our fantastic partners throughout 2025: AWS, Coinbase, EWC, HyperX, Mastercard, OMEN, Red Bull, Secretlab, and Verizon.

Make sure to follow the official VALORANT Esports social channels for additional information:
Twitter/X: @valorantesports
Facebook: /valorantesports
Instagram: @valorantesports
TikTok: @valorantesports
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/valorant
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@ValorantEsports
Photos from the Event: https://www.flickr.com/photos/valorantesports/

The 8 teams who make it out will be randomly seeded into a double elimination bracket, with teams from the same group placed on opposite sides of the bracket. Teams will compete through Best-of-3 matches until the final 2 matches which will be a Best-of-5. The last team standing will claim the title of VALORANT World Champion!

We’re proud to work with our fantastic partners throughout 2025: AWS, Coinbase, EWC, HyperX, Mastercard, OMEN, Red Bull, Secretlab, and Verizon.

snippet.description:
Buy NEW MERCH now, including the CHECKPOINT COMIC and G.U.I.D.O PLUSHIE!:
https://checkpointmerch.com

Check out the CHECKPOINT WEBSITE and make YOUR OWN Character!: https://checkpointmultiverse.com/

This is Minecraft But we're Upgrading Bloop Into a GOD In Minecraft! When Steve's body gets transformed into a Bloop he needs to UPGRADE himself by entering the mysterious portals! Steve needs to learn how to evolve himself to absurd levels so he can use the amazing overpowered upgrade abilities! Can Steve learn all the secrets and abilities of the evolution upgrades, get all the Bloop upgrades, and upgrade into the ultimate Bloop? This is Upgrading Bloop Into a GOD In Minecraft!
__

👋🏼 Checkpoint Website: https://checkpointmultiverse.com/
📸 Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/checkpoint.yt
❤️ Connect With Us: https://direct.me/checkpointmultiverse
🧑🏼‍🤝‍🧑🏼 Join the Community on Discord: https://discord.gg/jkfV7mSxB6

🎵 Additional Music provided by Epidemic Sound: https://www.epidemicsound.com/

MORE CHECKPOINT ADVENTURES:

‣ MINECRAFT DIMENSION: https://bit.ly/3mKfUOL


¬

Minecraft is an open world game that has no specific goals for the player to accomplish, allowing players a large amount of freedom in choosing how to play the game however, there is an achievement system. The gameplay by default is first person, but players have the option to play in third person mode. The core gameplay revolves around breaking and placing blocks. The game world is essentially composed of rough 3D objects—mainly cubes—that are arranged in a fixed grid pattern and represent different materials, such as dirt, stone, various ores, water, and tree trunks. While players can move freely across the world, objects and items can only be placed at fixed locations relative to the grid. Players can gather these material blocks and place them elsewhere, thus allowing for various constructions.

#Checkpoint #Minecraft
